question ‘What is one reason AI can weaken the security of an encrypted system, even if the encryption algorithm is strong?’

wrong ‘AI can automatically generate new encryption algorithms faster than humans’
wrong ‘AI can learn to reverse encryption without needing the key’
right ‘AI can guess weak passwords by identifying common patterns in user behavior’
wrong ‘AI can directly decrypt messages by analyzing metadata’

